meaning_str.bing:
n. 尝试；试图；企图；杀人企图
v. 尝试；试图；努力
网络. 袭击

尝试；试图；企图；杀人企图

尝试；努力；企图；试图；试图做；试图达成；试图完成；试图解决
（为超越某事物的）尝试；努力；企图；试图；挑战；尝试结果；试验；行动；举动

1.en: There was an attempt to sign up more men for the police force. but not many signed up.
1.cn: 警方本来打算雇用更多的人，但是报名参加的人不多。

2.en: Commanders at the scene clearly were aware of the widespread rapes, but there is no evidence that they made any attempt to stop them.
2.cn: 在现场的指挥官清楚地了解这些强奸，但没有证据表明他们做任何企图阻止其发生。

3.en: championed harsh local laws in an attempt to crack down on illegal immigration.
3.cn: 为了镇压非法移民，维护严苛的地方法律。

0.en: That was a joke, or an attempt at one. Next question.
0.cn: 那只是个笑话，或许是曾经有过的尝试，下一个问题。

1.en: We're going to attempt a manned mission. NASA said it would take five years.
1.cn: 我们准备尝试载人航天计划，航空航天局预计要花五年时间。

2.en: I'm going to attempt an experiment that will get you to transfer those feelings to me.
2.cn: 我准备尝试一个实验让你将这些情感转移到我身上。

3.en: Why didn't you attempt to return to LaGuardia? There simply was not enough altitude.
3.cn: 你为什么不尝试返回拉瓜迪亚机场？显然没有足够的高度。

4.en: And? And that means each iteration is an attempt to prove its own proof. It's recursive. It's nonsensical.
4.cn: 所以呢？这表示每一个迭代都只是在尝试自我证明，这是递归，是没有意义的。

5.en: The Hudson was the only place that was long enough and smooth enough and wide enough to even attempt to land the airplane safely.
5.cn: 只有哈德逊河足够长，足够平和足够宽，来冒险尝试把飞机安全降落。

6.en: Answer yes or no. Has there ever been, against my express instructions, any attempt at a psychiatric evaluation of Eurus Holmes?
6.cn: 回答是或不是，你们是否曾违反我的明确指令尝试对欧罗斯·福尔摩斯进行过精神鉴定。

7.en: If America Works succeeds, we will reinvent the American dream. If we fail in our attempt, we will admit it frankly and try another.
7.cn: 如果美国就业法案成功了，我们将彻底改造美国梦，如果我们的尝试失败，我们会坦白承认，然后重新来过。

8.en: Now, I will share with you the facts and evidence as they were available to me, and in this very room, you will all attempt to solve the case of Blessington The Poisoner.
8.cn: 我将告诉大家当时我已知的事实和证据，就在这里，大家可以尝试解开下毒者布莱辛顿之谜。

9.en: So, why attempt the impossible? Why follow your dream?
9.cn: 那为何要挑战不可能？为何要追寻梦想？

10.en: Any attempt on the director's life had to look successful.
10.cn: 为了让人觉得局长真的被谋杀了。

11.en: Mother and Father were terrified. They thought it was a suicide attempt.
11.cn: 我们的父母吓坏了。以为她是想自杀。

12.en: I'll attempt to access everyone in his inner circle. You stay on the number.
12.cn: 我要黑进他核心集团的每一个人，你盯紧号码。

13.en: I'm just sorry I'm not gonna be around to watch you two attempt to handle this.
13.cn: 真遗憾不能留下来看你照顾孩子手忙脚乱了。

14.en: Your unwillingness to accept empirical evidence suggests an attempt at flattery.
14.cn: 你不愿接受经验实据，说明一种奉承之举。

15.en: Nothing. It was a desperate attempt to introduce an alternate topic of conversation.
15.cn: 没关联，我只是迫切想为午餐会换个新话题罢了。

16.en: There was an assassination attempt in the fortress. Some tragedies were averted, some were not.
16.cn: 确实有人曾试图在宫中行刺，有些悲剧得以避免，有的没有。

17.en: Footage of the assassination attempt is still making its way to us, and we expect to have that shortly.
17.cn: 刺杀未遂事件的视频还没送到，但相信很快能够公布。

18.en: Now, Mr. Gardner will attempt to explain away this DNA in many exotic ways and in fact, like any good defense attorney.
18.cn: 加德纳先生会试着用许多特别的方法来为DNA辩解，实际上与任何优秀的辩护律师一样。

19.en: Philippe. My sons are consummate wire walkers. And I would never allow them to attempt such a walk without safety line.
19.cn: 菲利浦，我儿子都是高明的走钢索人，我绝不准他们不用安全索就上路。
